Class CountingUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.uniroma2.sel.simlab.jeqn.users.User
      • it.uniroma2.sel.simlab.jeqn.users.CountingUser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<User>

    public final class CountingUser
extends User
    Represents a user that incorporates counting capabilities, ie the user is provided with an internal counter. The counter can be incremented, tested, and reset using the class methods We need to investigate the differences with UserWithCounter
    Author:
    Daniele Gianni
